title: Ford GT 2016 WEC Silverstone: Race Highlights #FordWEC #6hSilverstone
description:
No spoilers in description! This is the story of the Ford GTs 2016 WEC opening round at Silverstone.
The Ford GT racecars made their European racing debut this weekend and despite a weekend featuring every season (yes, even snow) - the cars, team and fans enjoyed an awesome opener to the World Endurance Championship.  Please like, share and let us know what you think or what you'd like to see more of in the comments below!

Race day was 17th April (Qualis 16th April) 2016.
